  Ba 137.327 Ba_ONCV_PBE-1.2.upf
  Sn 118.71 Sn_ONCV_PBE-1.2.upf
ATOMIC_POSITIONS crystal
  Ba 0.000000 0.500000 0.500000
  Sn 0.865300 0.165573 0.699727
  Sn 0.500000 0.500000 0.000000
  Sn 0.134700 0.834427 0.300273
  Sn 0.534154 0.834427 0.699727
  Sn 0.465846 0.165573 0.300273
K_POINTS automatic
  24 24 24 0 0 0
